    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this immaculate specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle represents an uncompromising commitment to quality, featuring a pristine exterior and a cabin that remains in showroom condition. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting benchmarks for performance and reliability. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence, this offering provides a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of peerless pedigree. We invite serious inquiries to experience this benchmark of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
