    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or a speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it still drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels and smells brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
