    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade specimen that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, mirror-like paint finish completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent, with the premium leather seating surfaces showing zero bolster wear and the dashboard remaining pristine. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the mechanicals have been maintained with an open-checkbook policy\u2014complete with a comprehensive service history. From the untouched alloy wheels to the spotless undercarriage, this car offers the rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
