      "description": "Offering a superlative E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 powerplant. This high-revving, naturally aspirated engine utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and is mated to a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. This example is in collector-grade condition; the critical rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements have been performed preventatively to ensure mechanical longevity. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the original carbon fiber roof remains flawless, maintaining a low center of gravity. Every bushing and seal is tight, the M-Variable differential lock operates silently, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, investment-quality performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
